&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Loris demonstrated container monitoring with his relatively new tool &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.sysdig.org/"&gt;sysdig&lt;/a&gt;
and &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/google/cadvisor"&gt;cAdvisor&lt;/a&gt; from Google.  This is an excellent overview and demo of both
tools.  Additionally, Loris demos a commercial product that takes &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.sysdig.org/"&gt;sysdig&lt;/a&gt; to the
next level, providing a web based dashboard of an entire running cluster &amp;#8212;
&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://sysdig.com/"&gt;sysdig cloud&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
