&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rob presents an architectural overview of the Heka stream processing engine.  He
discusses some of its many use-cases.  This presentation will convey to the
viewer enough to determine if Heka is appropriate for potential&amp;nbsp;tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
